These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, 7up, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, reading, baking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, rock, techno, funk
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan funk##3
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is not the fan rock##6
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking 7up or the person who's hobby is reading is the fan techno, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking 7up and the fan folk have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan techno##3
 8. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the fan funk##5
 9. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | 7up   | milk      | soy-milk    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | reading | filmmaking | baking |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | folk | funk         | rock     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, pomegranate, asparagus, zucchini
There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, turkish, japanese
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, lizard, goat
 1. the german is the person eating zucchini or the owner of the goat is the german, but not both##10
 2. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
 3. the german is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 4. the owner of the lizard and the german have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
 9. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
11. the japanese is in an even position##4
12. the german is the person eating papaya or the german is the owner of the goat, but not both##10
13. the person eating papaya is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | zucchini | pomegranate    | papaya | asparagus    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | german | colombian  | japanese |
| Pet           | lizard     | goat    | cat    | chinchilla    |

