.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, soy-milk, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: corn, artichoke, peas, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, american, australian, turkish
1. the person eating avocado is the canadian##1
2. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
3. the person eating avocado is the turkish or the person eating avocado is the person drinking cola, but not both##10
4. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
5. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
6. the american is between the person eating corn and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | mirinda         | soy-milk     | cola | almond-milk |
| Food          | corn | artichoke | avocado         | peas   |
| Nationality   | australian     | american   | canadian       | turkish   |

