.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, corn, cranberry, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, hiking, card-games, dancing
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani, brazilian, malaysian
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the pakistani##1
 2. the nigerian is not to the right of the person eating cranberry##8
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the nigerian##6
 6. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person eating corn##5
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the brazilian or the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating corn, but not both##10
 8. the brazilian is the person eating cranberry or the brazilian is the person who's hobby is hiking, but not both##10
 9. the malaysian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person eating cranberry##7
10. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating plum##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | garlic  | plum   | corn | cranberry  |
| Hobby         | singing     | card-games  | hiking | dancing |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani | malaysian  | brazilian |

