.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, lemonade, 7up
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, disaster, sports, superhero
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, horse, pony
 1. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the bird is not the person watching disaster movies##6
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching western movies##2
 4. the person drinking sprite is not the person watching superhero movies##6
 5. the owner of the pony and the person watching western movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person watching western movies or the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the bird, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
11. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking 7up##7
12. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | 7up | sprite | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster    | western   | superhero |
| Pet           | bird    | guinea-pig | horse    | pony  |

