There are 4 different nationalities: polish, colombian, mexican, british
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, jet-ski, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 2. the polish is the person who's hobby is skydiving or the polish is the person driving the subway, but not both##10
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 4. the person driving the boat and the british have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the british is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 7. the colombian is on the far right##1
 8. the mexican is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the polish##7
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
10. the british is between the person driving the jet-ski and the mexican##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving   | sudoku | filmmaking  | fishing |
| Nationality   | polish  | mexican      | british | colombian |
| Transport     | skateboard | boat       | subway    | jet-ski   |

