.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, strawberry, onion, cauliflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, manager, police-officer, mechanic
4 different pets are kept: horse, snake, hedgehog, lizard
 1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
 2. the musician is between the owner of the horse and the person eating cauliflower##2
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 4. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person eating strawberry and the owner of the snake##7
 5. the owner of the snake and the person eating cabbage have the same parity positions##9
 6. the manager is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 7. the police-officer is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 9. the owner of the horse is the musician or the owner of the horse is the person eating onion, but not both##10
10. the owner of the horse and the manager have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
| Food   | onion    | cabbage     | cauliflower         | strawberry |
| Job    | manager | musician    | police-officer | mechanic    |
| Pet    | horse      | snake | hedgehog            | lizard   |

