.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-8::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, lettuce, cabbage, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, dancing, collecting, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, spy, scientific, crime
 1. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
 9. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
10. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is collecting or the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating cabbage, but not both##10
11. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | spinach     | cabbage     | mango    | lettuce  |
| Hobby         | woodworking | collecting  | dancing | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific      | crime | spy | epic |

