.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, pear, carrot, potato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, musical, scientific, satire
4 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, chinchilla, cat
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 2. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching scientific movies or the owner of the goldfish is the person eating apricot, but not both##10
